 du bouddhisme et dans le d\u00e9veloppement de l'Abhidharma|trans-title=A great disciple of the Buddha: S\u0101riputra, his role in Buddhist history and in the development of Abhidharma|journal=Bulletin de l'\u00c9cole fran\u00e7aise d'Extr\u00eame-Orient |date=1954|volume=46|issue=2|doi=10.3406/befeo.1954.5607|url=http://www.persee.fr/docAsPDF/befeo_0336-1519_1954_num_46_2_5607.pdf|language=fr}}\n* {{Citation |last=Minayev |first=I.P. |author-link=Ivan Minayev |year=1894 |title=Recherches sur le bouddhisme |publisher=Ernest Leroux |oclc=25136566 |language=fr |trans-title=Studies in Buddhism |url=https://archive.org/download/recherchessurleb00mina/recherchessurleb00mina.pdf |others=(originally in Russian)}}\n* {{Citation |last1=Morrison |first1=E. |title=The Power of Patriarchs: Qisong and Lineage in Chinese Buddhism |date=2010 |publisher=[[Brill Publishing]] |isbn=978-90-04-18301-8}}\n* {{Citation |last=Mukherjee |first=B. |year=1994 |title=The Riddle of the First Buddhist Council&nbsp;\u2013 A Retrospection |journal=Chung-Hwa Buddhist Journal |volume=7 |url=http://buddhism.lib.ntu.edu.tw/FULLTEXT/JR-BJ001/07_15.htm |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180917034346/http://buddhism.lib.ntu.edu.tw/FULLTEXT/JR-BJ001/07_15.htm |archive-date=17 September 2018 |url-status=live |pages=452{{en dash}}73}}\n* {{Citation |last1=Mun-keat |first1=Choong |title=A Comparison of the P\u0101li and Chinese Versions of the Kassapa Sa\u1e43yutta, a Collection Of Early Buddhist Discourses on the Venerable K\u0101\u015byapa |journal=[[Journal of the Royal Asiatic Society of Great Britain & Ireland]] |date=1 March 2017 |volume=27 |issue=2 |pages=295\u2013311 |doi=10.1017/S1356186316000559}}\n* {{Citation |last=Nattier |first=J. |author-link=Jan Nattier |year=1988 |chapter=The Meanings of the Maitreya Myth: A Typological Analysis |title=Maitreya, the Future Buddha |pages=23\u201347 |editor1-last=Sponberg |editor1-first=A. |editor2-last=Hardacre |editor2-first=H. |publisher=[[Cambri