binson-2010/ Official website of ''Expeditie Robinson'' at 2BE]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20101013062602/http://www.robinsonblog.nl/ Blog of ''Expeditie Robinson'' (Dutch)]\n* {{IMDb title|0261470|Expeditie Robinson}}\n\n{{Survivor}}\n\n[[Category:Dutch reality television series]]\n[[Category:Belgian reality television series]]\n[[Category:Survivor (franchise)]]\n[[Category:2000 Dutch television series debuts]]\n\n[[es:Supervivientes]]\n[[fr:Les Aventuriers de Koh-Lanta]]\n[[is:Survivor (sj\u00f3nvarps\u00fe\u00e1ttur)]]\n[[pl:Wyprawa Robinson]]\n[[pt:Survivor]]\n[[fi:Selviytyj\u00e4t]]\n[[sv:Expedition Robinson]]\n", "name_user": "WereSpielChequers", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eSeasons:Typo fixing, replaced: an other  \u2192  another", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Expeditie_Robinson"}
